Join Girl Scouts from around the council for the 3rd Annual Cookie Kickoff, now bigger and better than ever!! You'll learn about goal setting, managing money, safety, customer service, and more! Plus you'll receive tons of take homes, a very special Girl Scout tailgate and a ticket to the Jaguars game!
